WEBVTT

01:01.895 --> 01:04.939
EPISODE 10

01:33.885 --> 01:35.720
- No, talk with me instead.
- About what?

01:37.889 --> 01:40.600
Why should I hear you out
when you've been ghosting me?

01:40.683 --> 01:43.394
- Am I invisible?
- I could ask you the same thing.

01:44.020 --> 01:45.855
I wasn't joking when I said we're done.

01:45.939 --> 01:48.316
You ignored me,
even though I told you so many times,

01:48.650 --> 01:49.859
so don't yell at me.

01:50.360 --> 01:51.486
You have no right.

01:51.945 --> 01:53.780
Whatever I do, whomever I meet,

01:54.364 --> 01:56.241
you have no right to judge me.

01:57.075 --> 01:58.993
Why did you meet my father then?

01:59.077 --> 02:00.286
To tell him it was over.

02:00.995 --> 02:04.082
I told him that we failed as a couple.

02:13.800 --> 02:15.468
And that prick's your success story?

02:17.387 --> 02:19.556
You're mistaking pity for love.

02:19.639 --> 02:20.723
Watch your mouth.

02:22.475 --> 02:23.560
Ji-ho, no!

02:25.228 --> 02:26.980
Hey, I said you'd only get one pass.

02:27.730 --> 02:29.190
- Want to go at it then?
- Don't.

02:29.274 --> 02:31.359
- Get over here.
- Ji-ho, please let go!

02:31.442 --> 02:32.527
Stop it.

02:32.777 --> 02:34.320
- Don't.
- Let go of me.

02:35.113 --> 02:36.322
- Bring it on.
- Stop.

02:36.406 --> 02:38.283
- Come on. Do your worst.
- Ji-ho...

02:39.033 --> 02:40.910
- What are you waiting for?
- Hey!

02:42.745 --> 02:43.580
What?

02:43.705 --> 02:44.998
Wait for me in the car.

02:45.081 --> 02:46.124
Get over here!

02:51.129 --> 02:52.589
Hey, let go of me.

02:54.674 --> 02:55.633
Jeong-in.

02:56.551 --> 02:57.552
Jeong-in!

02:58.094 --> 02:59.012
Get back over here!

03:00.096 --> 03:02.640
Talk to me instead.
It's me you're pissed off at, anyway.

03:03.766 --> 03:06.102
- Let go of me.
- Maybe next time, all right?

03:07.145 --> 03:08.021
You're pushing it.

03:08.897 --> 03:10.523
Let's leave Jeong-in out of this.

03:11.983 --> 03:13.026
Stay back.

03:13.234 --> 03:15.570
- Don't!
- Get off me!

03:15.653 --> 03:18.489
- Just talk it out, all right?
- Get over here.

03:20.241 --> 03:21.701
Let go.

04:34.357 --> 04:36.693
Just a month after Eun-u was born...

04:38.611 --> 04:40.113
his mother disappeared.

04:42.782 --> 04:43.825
It made me furious.

04:45.118 --> 04:46.452
While searching for her,

04:46.953 --> 04:49.080
I promised myself I'd have a go at her.

04:50.665 --> 04:51.916
That's all I thought about.

04:53.793 --> 04:55.503
Worries swept over me as time passed.

04:57.922 --> 04:59.549
"What if she won't come back?

05:01.467 --> 05:03.469
Then how do I raise Eun-u alone?

05:06.723 --> 05:08.516
Do I have to give him up for adoption?"

05:14.772 --> 05:16.607
I stooped down so low

05:17.984 --> 05:19.402
because all I could think about

05:20.737 --> 05:22.113
was how desperate I was.

05:24.782 --> 05:26.534
It was only after a while...

05:28.578 --> 05:30.747
that I realized she had her reasons too.

05:32.707 --> 05:36.210
She could've been overwhelmed
to the point that I couldn't comprehend.

05:39.005 --> 05:40.590
I still couldn't understand her...

05:41.924 --> 05:43.968
but letting myself admit that much...

05:46.095 --> 05:47.597
set my heart at rest.

05:53.353 --> 05:55.855
When I said that we should
take our time...

05:57.482 --> 05:58.983
it's not because I'm generous

05:59.650 --> 06:01.402
or the nicest man alive.

06:03.071 --> 06:05.740
It's just that Gi-seok needs time
to let this sink in.

06:10.286 --> 06:13.498
Us being understanding and considerate
doesn't really matter to anyone.

06:14.332 --> 06:17.585
To others, I'm a woman
who's seeing two men,

06:18.628 --> 06:21.547
and you're the guy
coming onto a woman who's taken.

06:24.217 --> 06:25.760
Why should we be seen that way?

06:27.345 --> 06:28.429
I don't want that.

06:31.099 --> 06:32.850
I'd rather cut you from my life.

06:34.018 --> 06:35.561
I'm not one to put on a calm face

06:36.646 --> 06:38.314
when I'm exploding in the inside.

06:42.151 --> 06:44.821
Just like how you don't hold back
when it comes to Eun-u...

06:46.155 --> 06:47.949
I can't put up with it, while others...

06:48.533 --> 06:50.243
trample on my feelings and decisions.

06:51.828 --> 06:53.788
I'd rather face it and let it shatter...

06:54.914 --> 06:56.416
than avoid the situation.

07:00.044 --> 07:01.546
Then why did you stop me earlier?

07:04.257 --> 07:05.466
Because I was embarrassed.

07:06.843 --> 07:09.137
Two men were growling over one woman.

07:09.637 --> 07:12.723
Passersby would've thought
I'm some kind of princess

07:13.057 --> 07:15.101
or an heiress of a rich CEO.

07:15.685 --> 07:16.853
It looked ridiculous.

07:26.279 --> 07:27.238
You working tomorrow?

07:29.574 --> 07:30.408
No.

07:48.968 --> 07:49.802
What?

07:51.137 --> 07:52.930
How have you been?

07:53.848 --> 07:56.017
As if you care. What do you want?

07:57.268 --> 07:58.394
Come on.

07:59.103 --> 08:01.606
Oh, please. You're the one
who said you needed to study.

08:02.732 --> 08:03.983
Did you pass the exam?

08:07.945 --> 08:09.405
What's with your other arm?

08:11.240 --> 08:12.658
Is that your exam certificate?

08:13.159 --> 08:13.993
No.

08:16.287 --> 08:18.289
Don't tell me... you bought me flowers.

08:24.754 --> 08:27.548
I just saw some while I was passing by.

08:28.466 --> 08:29.300
How much was it?

08:30.510 --> 08:31.844
Well, 5,000 won.

08:31.928 --> 08:32.845
So it was 2,000 won.

08:32.929 --> 08:34.972
- In fact, 3,000 won.
- Don't you have to study?

08:36.224 --> 08:38.559
I studied hard today.
I was at the academy until now

08:38.643 --> 08:40.311
even when there weren't any classes.

08:41.354 --> 08:42.480
Good for you, I guess.

08:46.526 --> 08:47.860
So what are you doing here?

08:49.153 --> 08:50.821
You said I was getting in the way.

08:50.905 --> 08:51.781
When?

08:53.115 --> 08:56.494
I overreacted to the whole thing,
and now I feel bad about it.

08:57.245 --> 08:58.704
I was hoping to clear the air.

09:01.332 --> 09:02.375
Do you have some money?

09:02.458 --> 09:03.584
What? Money?

09:04.919 --> 09:07.088
I do. I have some left from buying...

09:07.797 --> 09:09.090
- the flowers.
- Save it.

09:10.383 --> 09:11.926
Let's go upstairs for some tea.

09:13.094 --> 09:13.928
I can't!

09:16.931 --> 09:19.016
How can I, after what it led to last time?

09:19.100 --> 09:20.142
I'd rather not.

09:21.310 --> 09:22.436
As if.

09:23.187 --> 09:24.480
I know about the pharmacist.

09:32.071 --> 09:34.448
Thanks. Wait, this is too much.

09:37.326 --> 09:38.286
It's for the flowers.

09:38.619 --> 09:39.579
Oh, right.

10:22.288 --> 10:23.914
- Here.
- Thank you.

10:25.833 --> 10:26.709
So...

10:28.210 --> 10:29.795
Where's your sister?

10:30.588 --> 10:31.797
With the pharmacist.

10:37.178 --> 10:38.929
Is his son something to be ashamed of?

10:40.890 --> 10:42.058
Why hide the truth?

10:42.933 --> 10:44.518
You don't have to, you know.

10:46.437 --> 10:48.981
Of course, I know that.
It's his personal life, though

10:49.065 --> 10:51.150
and not something to blabber about.

10:51.233 --> 10:52.526
Why are you being defensive?

10:53.736 --> 10:56.739
- I wasn't telling you off.
- I didn't say that.

11:01.035 --> 11:02.286
Ji-ho and...

11:05.623 --> 11:06.624
And what?

11:08.626 --> 11:11.629
Is it okay for your sister to be with him?

11:14.423 --> 11:16.133
Love isn't something you can control.

11:31.565 --> 11:33.526
Have you lived here since you were little?

11:35.152 --> 11:37.738
Yes, since elementary school.

11:38.531 --> 11:41.200
I see. You must've been a tidy boy.

11:42.868 --> 11:45.663
I would've been even if
my parents didn't run a dry cleaner's.

11:46.163 --> 11:48.040
My mother likes everything neat and tidy.

11:48.499 --> 11:49.458
I see.

11:50.793 --> 11:51.919
Who do you take after?

11:54.296 --> 11:56.340
My good qualities are from my parents,

11:57.341 --> 11:59.260
but the others I picked up myself.

12:02.847 --> 12:04.056
You're a sweet son.

12:06.100 --> 12:08.269
Hardly. I've caused them so much trouble.

12:12.690 --> 12:14.984
- Can we sit?
- Sure. Go ahead.

12:21.198 --> 12:23.826
This place feels oddly familiar.

12:25.119 --> 12:26.787
It brings back memories too.

12:29.790 --> 12:31.333
It's a familiar place, that's why.

12:32.293 --> 12:33.544
The pharmacy too?

12:35.337 --> 12:39.425
Come to think of it,
you've never felt like a stranger either.

12:42.052 --> 12:43.429
You were drunk that first day.

12:45.222 --> 12:46.390
Don't kill the mood.

12:47.600 --> 12:48.851
It was the opposite for me.

12:50.978 --> 12:53.397
I was fascinated by how innocent you were.

12:55.399 --> 12:56.650
Am I not anymore?

12:58.611 --> 13:00.404
That side of you has completely gone.

13:06.202 --> 13:07.703
There's some instant coffee here.

13:09.413 --> 13:10.956
I like the vibe of this place.

13:11.582 --> 13:13.042
A drink would be perfect.

13:15.586 --> 13:16.462
Would you like one?

13:18.130 --> 13:19.173
You have drinks here?

13:20.758 --> 13:21.592
Probably.

13:34.605 --> 13:35.481
Hold on.

13:36.857 --> 13:38.067
What did I do wrong?

13:40.986 --> 13:42.905
I did everything right by her...

13:43.739 --> 13:46.283
while we were dating.

13:47.493 --> 13:48.452
Jeez.

13:48.828 --> 13:50.955
Okay, sure. I've been to hostess bars

13:51.330 --> 13:53.457
and had a few drinks

13:53.541 --> 13:56.585
with some ladies
while out with my friends.

13:56.669 --> 13:58.879
But who hasn't in his life?

13:59.255 --> 14:00.798
Right? You've done it too.

14:01.090 --> 14:03.092
How's that important right now?

14:04.385 --> 14:06.428
So why the hell is this happening?

14:09.265 --> 14:11.433
Does her choosing Ji-ho make sense?

14:12.560 --> 14:13.978
She chose him over me.

14:15.688 --> 14:16.897
It's Yu Ji-ho.

14:17.231 --> 14:19.650
I lost to none other than Ji-ho.
Are you kidding me?

14:20.234 --> 14:21.569
Am I that pathetic?

14:22.695 --> 14:24.405
In what way is Ji-ho better than me?

14:24.822 --> 14:26.115
Damn it.

14:30.077 --> 14:32.288
Why is it Yu Ji-ho of all people?

14:33.706 --> 14:34.748
You prick.

14:37.418 --> 14:38.711
Am I wrong though?

14:39.545 --> 14:40.921
I didn't say anything.

14:41.380 --> 14:42.381
That bastard...

14:43.007 --> 14:46.051
He's a nobody, you know.

14:46.594 --> 14:47.845
Okay, fine.

14:48.929 --> 14:50.264
He's nothing.

14:50.931 --> 14:53.934
He's nothing compared to me.

14:54.518 --> 14:56.353
All right, I get it.

14:57.104 --> 14:59.815
- Damn it.
- I need to take a piss.

15:16.582 --> 15:17.583
Hello?

15:20.586 --> 15:22.463
What do you want from me?

15:27.593 --> 15:28.677
What do you mean?

15:29.637 --> 15:31.847
What is it that you truly want?

15:33.098 --> 15:35.184
Why didn't you tell me
what Jeong-in told you?

15:36.101 --> 15:36.936
Why?

15:37.853 --> 15:39.647
She said she wasn't going to marry me.

15:41.023 --> 15:42.900
Why didn't you tell me that?

15:43.859 --> 15:44.902
You're drunk.

15:44.985 --> 15:47.446
When you first gave us your blessing,

15:48.072 --> 15:49.782
I was even touched.

15:50.616 --> 15:53.035
Not knowing what she had said to you...

15:54.578 --> 15:56.121
I was over the moon.

15:56.497 --> 16:00.000
How could you make me look like a fool?

16:00.167 --> 16:02.461
You made a mockery out of me.

16:02.544 --> 16:05.089
You're drunk, so just head on home.

16:06.298 --> 16:09.051
You should've told me the truth.

16:10.552 --> 16:13.514
Instead of making me
read between the lines...

16:16.183 --> 16:18.978
you should've told me
what really happened.

16:20.104 --> 16:21.105
Gi-seok.

16:22.398 --> 16:24.274
Do you really need to hear

16:24.358 --> 16:27.403
that your girl doesn't want to marry you
from your old man?

16:28.362 --> 16:31.240
You've always been
embarrassed of me, haven't you?

16:35.869 --> 16:36.912
I know.

16:38.497 --> 16:41.625
You've never once been satisfied with me.

16:43.127 --> 16:44.211
I know that too.

16:46.380 --> 16:48.340
I take after Mom...

16:53.470 --> 16:56.098
and you see me as a coward.

16:58.183 --> 17:00.144
You think I'm nothing but a fool.

17:01.562 --> 17:03.605
I've known that
for as long as I can remember.

17:06.316 --> 17:07.359
Father...

17:10.279 --> 17:14.283
you only think that way
because you don't know me better.

17:15.534 --> 17:18.495
I'm not viewed as inferior, you know.

17:19.580 --> 17:20.831
Out in society,

17:21.790 --> 17:23.667
people look up to me.

17:24.793 --> 17:26.128
I'm not too bad.

17:29.423 --> 17:30.883
I bet that sounds pathetic too.

17:34.803 --> 17:37.264
Of course. It's not like you've ever...

17:38.766 --> 17:41.393
You always twist things
and let sarcasm take over.

17:42.895 --> 17:46.565
This is why I said
that Jeong-in is maturer than you.

17:47.066 --> 17:49.610
You're not levelheaded enough
to marry anyone.

17:50.110 --> 17:51.111
But I will.

17:53.113 --> 17:54.198
Just you wait and see.

17:55.574 --> 17:57.159
I will marry her no matter what.

17:59.328 --> 18:02.331
No matter who or what
tries to get in our way...

18:03.457 --> 18:04.875
I will marry Jeong-in.

18:09.379 --> 18:10.923
Jae-in told me...

18:12.466 --> 18:13.759
I should be selfish.

18:15.511 --> 18:19.139
She says nothing else matters
if it's to protect my true feelings.

18:22.142 --> 18:24.520
At first, I only thought
she said that to comfort me,

18:25.395 --> 18:26.480
but that wasn't it.

18:27.648 --> 18:29.066
That's how it should be.

18:30.776 --> 18:32.611
So I'm not going to feel guilty anymore.

18:37.449 --> 18:39.201
He's not mad because of the timing.

18:42.329 --> 18:44.081
He's humiliated because it's me.

18:45.999 --> 18:47.918
I'll be disappointed
if you're intimidated.

18:51.630 --> 18:53.549
How can I be when you have my back?

19:01.348 --> 19:02.558
You're smart, right?

19:04.852 --> 19:07.604
I will say this once and only once,

19:07.688 --> 19:08.772
so take it to heart.

19:13.235 --> 19:15.362
When I'm not satisfied with you,

19:16.029 --> 19:17.406
I'll call you out on the spot.

19:19.199 --> 19:21.910
My bursts of anger
might not seem reasonable,

19:22.536 --> 19:25.080
and I could say harsh words as well.

19:27.875 --> 19:28.959
When I do though,

19:30.169 --> 19:32.629
don't think that I'm being dismissive.

19:35.090 --> 19:36.967
Don't walk on eggshells around me either.

19:37.801 --> 19:39.261
Or I'll kick you to the curb.

19:51.106 --> 19:53.025
I didn't say this to please you, you know.

19:53.942 --> 19:55.068
It's important.

19:56.195 --> 19:57.362
So don't forget it.

20:00.908 --> 20:01.742
Okay?

20:08.040 --> 20:10.083
Look at you thinking of a way out.

20:11.543 --> 20:14.213
You only gave me a peck
so that you'd pass a breathalyzer.

20:47.621 --> 20:49.581
PYEONGCHANGSA LAUNDRY

21:02.010 --> 21:03.553
Why didn't you pick up your phone?

21:04.221 --> 21:05.180
What?

21:10.102 --> 21:11.395
What's going on?

21:12.771 --> 21:13.814
I...

21:14.481 --> 21:15.524
My gosh!

21:17.901 --> 21:19.611
What are you doing?

21:27.536 --> 21:28.578
What's going on?

21:29.246 --> 21:30.080
Hold on.

21:32.916 --> 21:34.960
PYEONGCHANGSA LAUNDRY

23:40.127 --> 23:40.961
Gosh.

23:42.295 --> 23:45.090
Why come to the library
if you're going to stay on your phone?

23:45.173 --> 23:46.508
You called me here.

23:48.051 --> 23:50.554
What good does
an expensive education abroad do

23:50.971 --> 23:52.806
when it's practically useless?

23:54.558 --> 23:56.476
I'll find something to do, so don't worry.

23:57.769 --> 23:59.980
You think way too highly of your talents.

24:00.564 --> 24:01.773
Anyway, that's that,

24:02.482 --> 24:04.484
but who's the guy Jeong-in's been seeing?

24:04.568 --> 24:06.403
- How should I know?
- Come on.

24:07.404 --> 24:08.822
I don't know him that well.

24:09.739 --> 24:12.701
Then tell me what you do know.

24:13.952 --> 24:16.413
This is Jeong-in's workplace,
so ask her yourself.

24:19.666 --> 24:23.545
You should tell me before
your father gets to the bottom of this.

24:24.671 --> 24:28.008
How can I help her out if I don't know?

24:29.009 --> 24:32.679
Do you think he'll ever let this slide?
You saw what happened that day.

24:33.513 --> 24:37.642
Your father was so startled
that he even forgot to scold you.

24:38.727 --> 24:39.603
Who is he?

24:40.479 --> 24:41.855
Tell me!

24:45.192 --> 24:46.151
He's a pharmacist.

24:46.735 --> 24:47.569
What?

24:48.069 --> 24:49.321
They're the same age too.

24:50.614 --> 24:51.948
That's all I know.

24:54.534 --> 24:56.786
- Then--
- I'm hungry. Let's eat.

24:56.870 --> 24:59.456
Wait, hold on. Hey!

24:59.539 --> 25:00.749
Jae-in!

25:02.042 --> 25:04.085
When should I pick up my clothes?

25:05.545 --> 25:09.841
Why is Jeong-in being this way?
I'm completely clueless.

25:13.220 --> 25:15.013
She won't say anything else

25:15.096 --> 25:17.933
apart from the fact that she likes him.

25:19.059 --> 25:21.520
Even you think there's
something going on, right?

25:21.603 --> 25:23.522
- I couldn't care less.
- Why you...

25:26.608 --> 25:28.026
Just let her be.

25:29.236 --> 25:31.112
Jeong-in always knows what she's doing.

25:31.196 --> 25:32.697
Of course, I know that.

25:33.240 --> 25:35.408
Still, it's not like her
to hide things from me,

25:35.492 --> 25:36.785
which is why this is weird.

25:38.328 --> 25:41.206
Can't you try to
pry some information out of her?

25:41.289 --> 25:42.582
Find out what's going on.

25:43.291 --> 25:46.086
Will you disapprove if he's not up to par?

25:47.921 --> 25:49.422
I will if I have to.

25:50.048 --> 25:51.383
Not Dad, but you?

25:52.133 --> 25:54.678
I can't let my daughter
make the wrong choice.

25:57.097 --> 25:59.015
In what way?

26:04.980 --> 26:06.273
Why are you staring at me?

26:07.691 --> 26:10.318
You're mostly open-minded, so this is new.

26:11.069 --> 26:12.070
It's unlike you.

26:14.698 --> 26:17.033
It's not like I'd actually say anything.

26:17.367 --> 26:19.119
I'm curious, that's all.

26:19.202 --> 26:22.038
Precisely. I know
you're not that kind of person.

26:26.334 --> 26:29.462
Wouldn't you get scolded first
once your mom finds out?

26:31.089 --> 26:32.299
That I can easily take.

26:32.966 --> 26:34.009
My dad's the problem.

26:35.468 --> 26:36.803
He's too hot-tempered.

26:38.305 --> 26:39.681
Does he get physical?

26:40.807 --> 26:41.850
He doesn't.

26:43.518 --> 26:44.644
But who knows...

26:45.478 --> 26:47.022
if he'll make history.

26:48.064 --> 26:49.816
Do you think he could beat up the guy?

26:52.235 --> 26:54.863
You're worried about yourself
and not Ji-ho, right?

26:55.655 --> 26:56.781
Look, that's just...

26:57.699 --> 26:59.826
You're getting way ahead of yourself.

27:00.076 --> 27:02.203
All right. Whatever you say.

27:11.963 --> 27:13.256
Kiss me and you're dead.

27:19.638 --> 27:21.973
Who else needs lunch?
Is five orders enough?

27:23.016 --> 27:25.852
- We'll share if there's not enough.
- All right.

27:26.186 --> 27:27.979
That'll be all. No drinks are needed.

27:28.730 --> 27:31.816
Three steak sandwiches
and two bulgogi sandwiches.

27:31.900 --> 27:33.276
And the salad. To go, right?

27:33.360 --> 27:34.194
- Yes.
- Yes.

27:45.830 --> 27:47.791
- Great. Thank you.
- You can wait over there.

27:47.874 --> 27:51.127
One Hawaiian seafood
and one seafood classic, please.

27:51.211 --> 27:53.338
The heart emoji
next to Gi-seok's name is gone.

27:57.467 --> 27:58.301
Here.

27:59.386 --> 28:00.220
What's this?

28:02.639 --> 28:03.848
Eun-u gave it to me.

28:03.932 --> 28:05.642
Eun-u? Who's that?

28:06.726 --> 28:07.811
Ji-ho's son?

28:09.437 --> 28:11.398
Hey, then those dinosaur books...

28:13.566 --> 28:15.443
That's right. I'm getting sneaky.

28:16.027 --> 28:18.446
Your nephew? Oh, please.

28:36.923 --> 28:39.217
- Hello?
- It's been a long time.

28:40.009 --> 28:41.845
Oh, hello.

28:42.512 --> 28:44.806
Were you surprised
to hear from me out of the blue?

28:45.557 --> 28:47.100
I knew you'd get in touch with me.

28:49.310 --> 28:51.730
My show is about to begin,
so I can't talk for long.

28:51.813 --> 28:53.022
Anything I can do for you?

28:54.107 --> 28:54.941
Well...

28:55.984 --> 28:58.778
I'd rather not talk about it
over the phone.

28:59.362 --> 29:01.114
I'd like to talk in person.

29:01.865 --> 29:04.075
Well, I can meet you anytime.

29:05.994 --> 29:08.204
- I have plans, so I should get going.
- Okay, bye.

29:08.580 --> 29:11.166
Ms. Wang! I'm off.

29:11.249 --> 29:13.418
- Okay, bye.
- See you tomorrow!

29:13.501 --> 29:14.544
- All right.
- Bye.

29:16.421 --> 29:19.299
ONLINE BANKING
FOR EVERY FINANCIAL MATTER

29:19.382 --> 29:21.050
ENTER YOUR PASSWORD

29:21.718 --> 29:23.261
Are you lending money to someone?

29:23.344 --> 29:24.512
No, it's for my father.

29:25.722 --> 29:26.723
What for?

29:27.515 --> 29:28.892
I stole something from him.

29:30.518 --> 29:32.187
What did you steal for 300,000 won?

29:32.645 --> 29:33.688
Some booze.

29:34.147 --> 29:35.732
Didn't you say he only drinks soju?

29:36.649 --> 29:39.444
- To make sure he doesn't tell Mom.
- I'm not following at all.

29:39.903 --> 29:42.906
Anyway, never lend money to anyone
even if it's a close friend.

29:43.239 --> 29:44.115
When did I?

29:45.116 --> 29:48.578
I know you've lent people money
and never got paid back on many occasions.

29:48.661 --> 29:50.872
That's why I can't stand
any of your friends...

29:51.372 --> 29:53.041
WOORI PHARMACY

29:53.124 --> 29:54.375
Hi.

29:55.126 --> 29:56.252
Oh, be careful.

30:00.256 --> 30:01.257
I mean...

30:02.467 --> 30:05.136
it's not like I set you up with Jeong-in
behind his back.

30:05.762 --> 30:08.389
Why is he always so mean to me these days?

30:08.807 --> 30:09.808
It pisses me off.

30:11.100 --> 30:12.310
Try to be understanding.

30:16.731 --> 30:18.316
So, are you really seeing her now?

30:23.196 --> 30:24.322
Dude.

30:25.573 --> 30:26.908
You're starting to scare me.

30:27.617 --> 30:29.035
Are you really my buddy, Ji-ho?

30:31.329 --> 30:33.414
Just think of it as you doing me a favor.

30:34.082 --> 30:35.041
Tolerate him, please.

30:37.293 --> 30:38.878
Yes, I get it.

30:39.838 --> 30:42.632
But he makes it obvious
even in front of other people at work.

30:42.715 --> 30:43.883
That's what's killing me.

30:50.098 --> 30:51.349
It'll get more stressful.

30:52.433 --> 30:54.018
Just try to be patient with him.

30:54.102 --> 30:56.771
Jeez, what is this?
The arrogance of the winner?

30:57.730 --> 30:59.107
Why are you worried about him?

31:00.066 --> 31:02.652
I'm not worried.
I just understand how he must be feeling.

31:06.948 --> 31:08.908
Is this a "Love your enemies"
kind of thing?

31:10.577 --> 31:13.246
You see, he may perceive this

31:14.163 --> 31:16.499
as you gloating.

31:18.001 --> 31:19.210
That is out of my control.

31:22.797 --> 31:24.215
You're a weirdo.

31:29.220 --> 31:31.556
- I'm okay.
- Gosh, eat slowly.

31:35.727 --> 31:36.728
Thanks for this.

31:39.439 --> 31:41.733
Your cappuccino is ready!

31:42.275 --> 31:43.610
Jeong-in does that too.

31:44.944 --> 31:45.778
What?

31:46.571 --> 31:47.864
You sound just like her.

31:49.574 --> 31:51.492
We're sisters, so I'm sure we're similar.

31:52.619 --> 31:53.494
Right.

31:54.829 --> 31:56.915
You wanted to see me
because of Si-hoon, right?

31:56.998 --> 31:59.042
Here's what you ordered.

32:00.001 --> 32:02.003
I know about the loan.

32:05.048 --> 32:05.965
Oh, that...

32:06.799 --> 32:09.928
There's nothing I can do to help him,

32:10.428 --> 32:11.888
and I've explained that to him.

32:14.849 --> 32:16.601
Then why did you want to see me?

32:19.687 --> 32:20.647
Because of Jeong-in?

32:21.898 --> 32:22.732
Yes.

32:26.444 --> 32:27.820
I don't know the details,

32:28.571 --> 32:30.073
but I can gather what's going on.

32:30.865 --> 32:31.699
But I think...

32:32.575 --> 32:34.243
you're talking to the wrong person.

32:35.453 --> 32:37.538
Jeong-in and I are very close...

32:38.247 --> 32:40.792
but I don't like to stick my nose
into her personal life.

32:41.417 --> 32:42.877
She wouldn't want that either.

32:42.961 --> 32:46.506
It's one of the things
that Jeong-in is sensitive about.

32:47.507 --> 32:48.758
So I understand.

32:52.637 --> 32:53.930
But about what's going on...

32:56.641 --> 32:58.434
It's not something I can let slide.

33:00.520 --> 33:03.898
I know that she trusts you
and respects your opinion the most,

33:04.816 --> 33:06.943
so I wanted to talk to you
about it in person.

33:08.152 --> 33:10.697
Your iced Americano is ready.

33:18.871 --> 33:19.956
Things between us...

33:21.958 --> 33:23.334
are very rocky at the moment.

33:32.677 --> 33:33.803
Do you believe...

33:35.388 --> 33:37.098
this can be remedied?

33:40.768 --> 33:42.061
Does it seem impossible?

33:44.647 --> 33:46.107
What is it that you want to say?

33:47.275 --> 33:49.861
Are you here to ask me
to help you mend your relationship?

33:51.320 --> 33:54.157
Shouldn't you figure it out on your own?

33:59.203 --> 34:00.413
Gosh, this is...

34:11.674 --> 34:13.718
She has feelings for someone.

34:14.552 --> 34:15.428
Another guy.

34:18.264 --> 34:20.641
You're not asking me
to stop that, are you?

34:22.685 --> 34:23.686
You knew about it?

34:28.524 --> 34:31.027
It must be hurtful for you.

34:32.153 --> 34:32.987
But you see...

34:34.363 --> 34:37.575
I don't think anything will change,
even if I get involved.

34:39.952 --> 34:41.162
And as her sister...

34:42.413 --> 34:45.166
I should respect her decision.

34:47.960 --> 34:49.504
What if he's a single father?

34:58.429 --> 35:00.890
The man she's seeing has a son.

35:03.434 --> 35:04.727
He's a single dad.

35:12.276 --> 35:15.113
Mending our relationship comes second.

35:16.447 --> 35:18.783
We must dissuade her
from getting involved with him.

35:20.326 --> 35:23.162
She's not in her right mind.
I can't let her be.

35:30.211 --> 35:31.087
SEO-IN

35:34.924 --> 35:37.260
I met Gi-seok earlier today.
Can you come over now?

35:37.802 --> 35:38.886
I sure did.

35:38.970 --> 35:39.804
- Really?
- Yes.

35:39.887 --> 35:41.806
I have to go see Seo-in now.

35:41.889 --> 35:43.099
- Why?
- Enjoy the food.

35:43.975 --> 35:45.059
See you.

35:49.480 --> 35:50.523
I don't know.

37:55.356 --> 37:57.316
At first,
the idea itself was inconceivable.

37:59.986 --> 38:02.446
Regardless of whether
I break up with Gi-seok or not...

38:03.906 --> 38:07.243
I didn't even dream of doing anything
with him.

38:09.453 --> 38:10.288
But...

38:12.707 --> 38:13.541
I realized...

38:15.042 --> 38:16.711
that I kept looking for him.

38:19.797 --> 38:21.132
Even though he kept...

38:22.717 --> 38:24.010
pushing me away...

38:27.555 --> 38:30.391
I clung to him... more.

38:34.270 --> 38:36.022
Yes, you can develop feelings for him.

38:38.274 --> 38:39.692
I understand that part, but...

38:40.484 --> 38:41.319
It's Eun-u.

38:42.570 --> 38:43.571
That's his son's name.

38:46.115 --> 38:46.949
I see.

38:50.369 --> 38:51.662
I may be feeling this way...

38:54.081 --> 38:55.791
because I like him.

38:57.376 --> 39:00.254
Or perhaps, it's just because of
my natural affinity with kids.

39:02.381 --> 39:04.300
I don't know the answer yet.

39:09.930 --> 39:10.848
Whatever it is...

39:15.644 --> 39:16.479
I adore...

39:18.064 --> 39:18.981
Eun-u.

39:23.277 --> 39:25.404
I don't even know
when I began feeling this way.

39:27.698 --> 39:29.116
I found myself cherishing him.

39:34.872 --> 39:35.706
I'm sorry.

39:38.292 --> 39:40.461
I'm sorry I couldn't tell you sooner...

39:45.257 --> 39:46.842
and for worrying you like this too.

39:48.302 --> 39:49.762
I'm really sorry for everything.

39:57.269 --> 39:58.104
Seo-in.

40:04.151 --> 40:05.403
I'll sort everything out.

40:06.904 --> 40:07.738
Okay?

40:11.367 --> 40:12.743
I'm not upset.

40:15.204 --> 40:16.288
I'm ashamed.

40:22.378 --> 40:23.629
I'm pregnant.

40:28.509 --> 40:29.760
I was going to give it up.

40:30.803 --> 40:32.221
It's too cruel, you know.

40:33.472 --> 40:34.306
And...

40:36.600 --> 40:37.977
I even thought of...

40:41.772 --> 40:43.732
that innocent baby as a punishment.

40:45.860 --> 40:47.236
But how could you...

40:57.037 --> 40:58.164
You will be...

40:59.498 --> 41:00.583
a great mom.

41:02.626 --> 41:03.836
You'll figure it all out.

41:06.297 --> 41:07.339
You have to.

41:11.385 --> 41:12.344
Okay.

41:14.597 --> 41:15.473
Gosh.

41:38.287 --> 41:39.538
This is my sister.

41:39.622 --> 41:40.706
Oh, hello.

41:42.333 --> 41:43.876
It's nice to meet you, Ji-ho.

41:46.462 --> 41:47.838
Thank you. Likewise.

41:48.589 --> 41:49.507
And...

41:50.966 --> 41:51.967
I'm sorry.

41:54.887 --> 41:56.430
I'll pretend I didn't hear that.

41:59.099 --> 42:00.142
Thank you.

42:02.603 --> 42:03.938
By the way, why are you here?

42:05.147 --> 42:06.148
Oh, I was just...

42:06.732 --> 42:08.776
- Did you want to see this news anchor?
- Hey.

42:10.945 --> 42:12.196
So, what do you think?

42:12.821 --> 42:13.948
Is she prettier than me?

42:16.742 --> 42:19.662
Come to think of it,
you've never said I'm pretty.

42:20.955 --> 42:23.415
Really? Jeong-in is pretty.

42:23.541 --> 42:25.751
I know. That's why I like her.

42:26.210 --> 42:27.836
- You said you love me.
- Yes.

42:40.182 --> 42:43.227
I actually regret
not telling Seo-in sooner.

42:44.270 --> 42:46.063
I was so worried while waiting outside.

42:47.314 --> 42:48.899
I told you not to wait for me.

42:50.651 --> 42:53.279
It was because of me,
so it'd be irresponsible to take off.

42:54.572 --> 42:56.657
I must say, you're such a smooth talker.

42:57.533 --> 42:59.243
I'll even get smacked on your behalf.

42:59.326 --> 43:01.996
Who'd dare to smack me?
Do you think I'd hold myself back?

43:03.581 --> 43:06.083
Don't judge a book by its cover.
I'm very strong.

43:07.960 --> 43:09.044
Okay, I'll be careful.

43:12.548 --> 43:13.757
I mean it though.

43:15.926 --> 43:17.094
I won't let you get hurt.

43:20.931 --> 43:22.683
I'm touched by just hearing that...

43:23.892 --> 43:25.728
so don't try to handle everything alone.

43:26.228 --> 43:28.188
And how can I just sit back and watch?

43:29.356 --> 43:30.899
You told me not to be a loser.

43:31.942 --> 43:33.569
So, you do take my advice.

43:35.070 --> 43:36.405
I don't want to get smacked.

43:36.488 --> 43:38.073
Behave yourself, Ji-ho.

43:39.783 --> 43:40.909
I will, Jeong-in.

43:43.704 --> 43:44.747
So?

43:45.456 --> 43:46.832
Am I pretty or not?

43:48.751 --> 43:50.169
It's getting late. Let's go.

43:51.045 --> 43:52.087
Look at you.

43:53.464 --> 43:55.966
- And you still expect a compliment?
- What? Come on.

43:56.800 --> 43:59.219
So, I'm not pretty?
You don't think I'm pretty?

43:59.303 --> 44:00.429
We should get going.

44:01.597 --> 44:03.307
You're not going to say it? Fine.

44:05.434 --> 44:07.728
I didn't think Gi-seok
would stoop this low.

44:08.437 --> 44:10.564
He's as much of a loser as Si-hoon is.

44:11.065 --> 44:12.816
Why didn't he just tell on Mom or Dad?

44:13.025 --> 44:15.611
I should leave 30 minutes early tomorrow
for the meeting.

44:15.694 --> 44:16.987
You shouldn't let it slide.

44:17.279 --> 44:18.989
Tell him to stop or something.

44:21.158 --> 44:22.576
That's what he wants.

44:28.582 --> 44:30.709
I used to get all angry
and meet him in person,

44:31.543 --> 44:33.796
then we'd end up getting back together.

44:34.088 --> 44:35.881
He thinks it'll happen again this time.

44:37.341 --> 44:40.260
I bet he's in disbelief now
because he didn't get a call from me.

44:41.804 --> 44:44.640
Whether it's his strategy or not,
will you just let it slide?

44:46.225 --> 44:47.476
Both Seo-in...

44:48.477 --> 44:50.979
and Ji-ho think
I shouldn't do anything to provoke him.

44:51.355 --> 44:54.274
- So what? Wait until he gives up?
- He won't give up that easily.

44:56.318 --> 44:58.529
Will he seek out both Mom and Dad?

44:59.613 --> 45:01.907
I should tell Mom and Dad
before it gets to that.

45:03.033 --> 45:03.867
Jeong-in.

45:04.785 --> 45:06.245
You might get killed.

45:07.621 --> 45:09.498
I'm prepared for the worst-case scenario.

45:25.639 --> 45:27.057
- Will you be all right?
- Yes.

45:28.350 --> 45:29.476
Go back inside.

45:30.936 --> 45:33.188
- Hey, I'll hail a taxi for you.
- No, don't worry.

45:33.564 --> 45:34.815
- Let me do it.
- It's okay.

45:34.898 --> 45:36.817
I'm off. Bye.

46:00.215 --> 46:02.885
- Isn't she a news anchor?
- Yes, sir. She is.

46:08.432 --> 46:10.225
What is this place? Is it a bar?

46:10.559 --> 46:15.105
Yes, sir.
It's known as a hangout for musicians.

46:26.325 --> 46:28.327
PRINCIPAL LEE TAE-HAK

46:30.829 --> 46:33.165
- Hello?
- Let's grab lunch together somewhere.

46:37.544 --> 46:39.755
- Oh, well...
- Do you have other plans?

46:41.840 --> 46:44.927
- Yes, I'm sorry.
- Don't be. All right, then.

46:54.353 --> 46:56.730
- Take it before meals.
- Okay, have a nice day.

46:56.814 --> 46:58.524
- You too. Bye.
- Thank you. Bye.

47:02.194 --> 47:03.529
I've been on my feet all day.

47:04.321 --> 47:05.364
You must be tired.

47:05.572 --> 47:07.699
I don't know why,
but we are busier these days.

47:08.116 --> 47:10.285
Now that Ji-ho is on a path to happiness,

47:10.369 --> 47:12.204
I have to do more work.

47:12.871 --> 47:14.122
What kind of logic is that?

47:14.456 --> 47:16.458
- Send this off with our order.
- Got it.

47:17.668 --> 47:18.794
I'm just happy for you.

47:18.877 --> 47:21.463
Hey, no one else cares about you
as much as I do.

47:22.130 --> 47:24.800
That's true. Every time
we have lunch together, she says,

47:24.883 --> 47:26.802
"Ji-ho deserves to be happy.

47:26.885 --> 47:30.013
I hope only good things await him."
She's always so worried about you.

47:30.514 --> 47:31.515
You're all talk.

47:32.975 --> 47:34.268
So, when's Jeong-in coming?

47:34.935 --> 47:35.769
Why?

47:35.853 --> 47:37.062
I want to see her.

47:38.355 --> 47:39.273
Maybe another day.

47:39.356 --> 47:41.316
Come on! Tell her to come today.

47:43.193 --> 47:45.946
Because of what you told her,
she thinks I have many secrets.

47:46.655 --> 47:48.407
You are the worst guy, indeed.

47:48.949 --> 47:50.659
- Why?
- I can go on and on.

47:51.201 --> 47:53.996
You're such a dutiful son.
From the money issue to your exes--

47:54.079 --> 47:55.497
Hye-jeong, please.

47:57.249 --> 47:58.625
- So, when can I see her?
- What?

48:14.266 --> 48:17.811
Hey, Ji-ho wants me to meet
the pharmacist he works with.

48:18.604 --> 48:20.898
You're getting to know
the people around him.

48:20.981 --> 48:22.065
You should come too.

48:22.774 --> 48:23.817
Me? Why?

48:24.151 --> 48:26.236
He's bringing a supporter.

48:26.737 --> 48:27.946
Are you going to ditch me?

48:28.363 --> 48:30.866
Hey, I never said I'm in support of this.

48:31.950 --> 48:34.578
I have to persuade my parents.
Must you add to that stress?

48:35.120 --> 48:36.997
Why are you leaving out Ji-ho's parents?

48:37.497 --> 48:39.458
There's no guarantee
that they'll like you.

48:40.250 --> 48:44.046
Well, they at least won't treat you as if
you don't exist, unlike Gi-seok's parents.

48:45.631 --> 48:47.633
The way they treated me
made me so miserable.

48:48.800 --> 48:50.636
Ji-ho will have it a lot tougher, right?

48:52.429 --> 48:55.057
Don't worry about that yet.
It'll only wear you out.

48:56.558 --> 48:57.851
So you'll help me, right?

48:58.393 --> 49:00.604
I'm going to help Ha-rin first.

49:01.563 --> 49:03.941
Hey, are you really going to be like this?

49:05.567 --> 49:06.818
I can do this by myself.

49:07.527 --> 49:09.363
Then you shouldn't have whined about it.

49:09.613 --> 49:11.448
Yeong-ju was going to come down as well.

49:14.284 --> 49:16.203
I've never worked with a book club before,

49:16.411 --> 49:18.330
and I'm extra nervous
because they're kids.

49:19.539 --> 49:22.918
I heard kids can actually tell
whether you're a good person or not.

49:25.045 --> 49:27.381
In my sister's experience
of raising her own kids,

49:28.090 --> 49:30.801
she's learned that children are indeed
our greatest mirrors.

49:31.593 --> 49:33.595
She said you can never fool kids.

49:34.596 --> 49:36.014
They don't want to be hated,

49:36.098 --> 49:38.558
so they don't say anything
even if they don't like you.

49:40.727 --> 49:43.313
That means they can pretend
they like you when they don't.

49:43.522 --> 49:44.523
Yes, of course.

49:48.402 --> 49:50.153
Why do you suddenly look all serious?

49:51.196 --> 49:52.364
What? It's nothing.

49:58.328 --> 50:00.330
- Did you have fun?
- Yes.

50:05.585 --> 50:08.171
Eun-u, it's too dusty here.

50:08.630 --> 50:10.966
Take Grandpa's phone and go home.

50:12.342 --> 50:14.511
- I'll follow you shortly.
- Okay.

50:16.805 --> 50:21.643
Well, we have so many masks.
Why don't you use them?

50:22.185 --> 50:23.103
You should use them.

50:25.272 --> 50:26.356
Why is this stuck?

50:31.403 --> 50:33.363
I only had a shot of it the other day.

50:34.906 --> 50:37.325
Was the shot glass as big as a bowl?

50:39.661 --> 50:40.579
What?

50:42.080 --> 50:43.331
When did I drink this much?

50:43.999 --> 50:46.168
Goodness, you kill me.

50:46.793 --> 50:47.878
My goodness.

51:02.350 --> 51:03.643
Best of luck.

51:15.572 --> 51:17.032
Mr. Kwon, here.

51:17.908 --> 51:20.368
- These were left out. Please go through--
- I heard you.

51:23.580 --> 51:26.583
The team manager wants to review them
first thing tomorrow morning.

51:31.129 --> 51:33.590
- Are you giving me orders now?
- No, I'm not.

51:36.802 --> 51:37.844
I'm sorry.

51:56.363 --> 51:57.364
Hey, Gi-seok.

51:57.447 --> 51:59.658
Hi, can you talk now?

52:00.158 --> 52:01.201
Yes, for a few minutes.

52:01.660 --> 52:04.871
Okay. I was wondering
what your schedule is like for today.

52:05.747 --> 52:06.581
Why do you ask?

52:07.707 --> 52:09.084
I haven't seen you in a while,

52:09.167 --> 52:13.130
and I need to talk to you about
the loan as well.

52:14.089 --> 52:15.715
Well, today is...

52:17.843 --> 52:20.846
If you're busy,
we can meet up another day.

52:22.514 --> 52:23.723
Is it because of Jeong-in?

52:25.267 --> 52:26.143
Sorry?

52:26.226 --> 52:29.229
I met Father. He seemed worried about you.

52:31.439 --> 52:32.440
About what?

52:33.358 --> 52:35.318
About your marriage, of course.

52:41.074 --> 52:42.784
I probably should talk to him soon.

52:52.002 --> 52:52.919
Hello.

53:03.597 --> 53:05.223
- You had a late lunch today.
- Yes.

53:05.974 --> 53:07.934
Oh, Mr. Kwon
already took care of your bill.

53:08.393 --> 53:09.227
Sorry?

53:10.353 --> 53:14.232
He left just after you arrived.

53:15.609 --> 53:16.610
My goodness.

53:22.240 --> 53:23.325
Oh, boy.

53:23.408 --> 53:25.118
CHIEF DIRECTOR'S OFFICE

53:31.583 --> 53:32.876
- Are you here to see me?
- Oh!

53:33.585 --> 53:37.088
Yes, I heard you paid for my lunch.

53:37.923 --> 53:41.343
Well, I saw you came alone
when you told me you had plans.

53:41.509 --> 53:43.720
I thought you were upset with me
about something

53:43.803 --> 53:45.388
and left quietly.

53:51.311 --> 53:55.357
What happened was,
my plans suddenly got canceled.

53:56.316 --> 54:00.070
You should've called me
even if it happened at the last minute.

54:06.284 --> 54:10.455
I think your daughter
may be seeing someone else.

54:11.831 --> 54:14.459
I just had an inkling,
but I suppose it's actually true.

54:15.919 --> 54:17.587
No, I never heard anything about it.

54:18.880 --> 54:21.675
Who told you such nonsense?

54:21.758 --> 54:23.009
So you don't know about it?

54:23.635 --> 54:25.262
What's there to know about?

54:26.346 --> 54:30.308
You're saying this because you don't know
what my daughter is like.

54:30.934 --> 54:32.644
She's such an upright person,

54:33.144 --> 54:35.438
so she'd never do such a thing.

54:38.441 --> 54:41.444
By the way, what exactly did you hear?

54:42.988 --> 54:44.906
Just based on the circumstances.

54:46.992 --> 54:49.494
Your daughter
doesn't want to marry Gi-seok.

54:49.703 --> 54:50.745
Did you know?

54:52.038 --> 54:54.833
Well, she's just saying that.

54:57.168 --> 55:00.714
I mean, many young people these days
don't believe in marriage.

55:01.172 --> 55:03.216
I think that's why she said that to you.

55:03.717 --> 55:06.261
I'm sure Gi-seok doesn't love
everything about it either.

55:08.263 --> 55:11.349
Things aren't like
how they used to be back in our day.

55:12.350 --> 55:14.519
You always emphasize that yourself.
My goodness.

55:19.274 --> 55:22.569
So you're sure
she's not seeing someone else?

55:23.320 --> 55:24.446
Yes, I'm sure.

55:24.863 --> 55:27.907
I'm telling you.
She'd never do such a thing.

55:29.743 --> 55:31.619
You look like you're in a job interview.

55:31.703 --> 55:33.079
No, I'm totally comfortable.

55:33.872 --> 55:35.999
- Ji-ho is...
- What? What are you going to say?

55:37.250 --> 55:38.960
I haven't even said anything yet.

55:39.336 --> 55:40.503
What about him?

55:41.713 --> 55:43.965
His specialty is doing things
that women hate.

55:45.008 --> 55:48.136
I mean, he can lend money to his friends.

55:48.219 --> 55:50.263
They're his friends, so I get it.

55:51.056 --> 55:53.516
The issue is, he doesn't bother
getting the money back.

55:53.600 --> 55:57.479
- That would drive me nuts.
- Yeong-ju, hear me out.

55:57.729 --> 55:58.563
What else?

55:58.646 --> 56:00.732
Be it a pal, a classmate,
or a friend's friend.

56:00.815 --> 56:03.193
He pays for everything
whenever he hangs with anyone.

56:04.402 --> 56:06.488
- Not all the time.
- Be quiet.

56:06.821 --> 56:09.908
And he's like Santa Claus
to all the ladies.

56:11.159 --> 56:12.410
What are you talking about?

56:12.952 --> 56:16.247
You buy them birthday and Christmas gifts
whenever they bring it up.

56:16.331 --> 56:18.124
Goodness. Just call it quits, Jeong-in.

56:18.708 --> 56:21.294
No, she's exaggerating it
because she's drunk now.

56:21.961 --> 56:23.296
Shall I call them, then?

56:23.380 --> 56:24.839
What? Call who?

56:24.923 --> 56:26.508
You're not helping me at all here.

56:28.927 --> 56:31.763
Jeong-in, you know
what I'm trying to tell you, right?

56:32.597 --> 56:34.599
Yes, I sure do. Don't worry.

56:35.558 --> 56:38.520
Disciplining him will be a piece of cake.

56:40.105 --> 56:41.231
I like you.

56:54.536 --> 56:56.788
- Are you going somewhere?
- I want some fresh air.

56:57.372 --> 56:59.374
What's wrong?
Is your stomach upset?

56:59.999 --> 57:01.751
- Shall I come with you?
- No, it's okay.

57:23.690 --> 57:24.899
Hello!

57:44.502 --> 57:46.212
- Oh, no. Let me pour you one.
- Okay.

57:48.423 --> 57:49.507
Thank you.

57:50.425 --> 57:52.427
So? Is the talk about marriage...

57:53.636 --> 57:54.846
going well?

57:57.432 --> 57:58.433
Well, so-so.

58:00.977 --> 58:03.730
How come you guys never seem passionate?

58:09.235 --> 58:12.906
By the way, how much money do you need?

58:15.533 --> 58:18.703
Well, it's tricky to get approved
for a loan,

58:18.786 --> 58:21.873
but I figured I could help you personally.

58:27.962 --> 58:29.130
Here is what you ordered.

58:34.302 --> 58:35.303
You have some money...

58:37.722 --> 58:38.932
No, it's not that.

58:39.557 --> 58:43.394
I just think
I may be able to help you out a little.

58:43.478 --> 58:45.313
- Eat this.
- Thank you.

58:48.900 --> 58:50.610
- The food is good here. Eat up.
- Okay.

59:01.120 --> 59:03.248
Did I offend you by any chance?

59:11.339 --> 59:13.341
I don't need any money.
Or that loan.

59:17.428 --> 59:20.348
I see. Then are you all ready now?

59:21.975 --> 59:23.977
My wife will divorce me
if I take out a loan.

59:31.943 --> 59:34.070
When you're married,
you have to obey your wife.

59:35.280 --> 59:36.573
Thanks for your help anyway.

59:41.619 --> 59:42.870
I won't bug you anymore.

59:43.413 --> 59:45.456
Gosh, don't say that.

59:51.296 --> 59:52.755
She's even done something worse.

59:53.256 --> 59:54.882
- You're so chatty today.
- Be quiet.

59:56.426 --> 01:00:00.263
When my body temperature was hovering
at 40 degrees because of a cold,

01:00:00.346 --> 01:00:03.016
Jeong-in watched a movie on her laptop

01:00:03.099 --> 01:00:05.935
and drank beer right next to me

01:00:06.019 --> 01:00:07.562
without even batting an eye.

01:00:08.563 --> 01:00:11.274
Jeez, that is simply unacceptable.

01:00:11.441 --> 01:00:13.526
I guess Jeong-in isn't
the affectionate type.

01:00:13.610 --> 01:00:15.945
- Exactly!
- She's not affectionate. She sure isn't.

01:00:17.030 --> 01:00:18.698
So what? You don't like me now?

01:00:19.115 --> 01:00:21.784
- I like you despite that.
- Even if I'm not affectionate?

01:00:21.868 --> 01:00:23.369
It's fine cos I'm affectionate.

01:01:57.255 --> 01:01:58.423
The door is opening.

01:02:01.926 --> 01:02:02.885
Bye.

01:02:07.390 --> 01:02:08.599
The door is closing.

01:02:14.313 --> 01:02:15.356
Going up.

01:02:16.357 --> 01:02:17.608
The door is closing.

01:02:23.781 --> 01:02:25.700
See? I told you.

01:03:15.708 --> 01:03:17.668
Gi-seok is meeting my dad?

01:03:17.877 --> 01:03:19.670
Ji-ho, I'll handle this.

01:03:19.754 --> 01:03:22.006
Until when do I have to hide behind you?

01:03:22.089 --> 01:03:24.884
I don't plan to let Gi-seok
have his way indefinitely.

01:03:24.967 --> 01:03:27.011
Being understanding and patient
isn't working.

01:03:27.094 --> 01:03:28.763
His goal is to take me down.

01:03:28.846 --> 01:03:31.974
Neither Gi-seok nor your father
will back down easily.

01:03:32.058 --> 01:03:33.267
Gi-seok won't stay quiet.

01:03:33.351 --> 01:03:36.979
I think you should decide
on the date for us.

01:03:37.063 --> 01:03:39.106
As they say,
"Strike while the iron is hot."

01:03:39.607 --> 01:03:41.567
Let's nail down a date
for their wedding.

01:03:41.651 --> 01:03:43.361
It looks like you already know.

01:03:43.569 --> 01:03:45.613
Don't jump to your own conclusions though.

01:03:45.696 --> 01:03:47.990
I'll never avoid running into Ji-ho.

01:03:48.074 --> 01:03:49.367
You must know what it means.

01:03:49.826 --> 01:03:52.036
Let's go somewhere fun with Eun-u.

01:03:53.037 --> 01:03:56.040
I see that you're touched again.
You're seriously too easy.

01:03:56.499 --> 01:03:58.084
Thank you, God.

01:03:58.543 --> 01:04:00.461
I'm in love.

01:04:03.756 --> 01:04:05.758
Subtitle translation by Hye-lim Park
